{
  "receptionist|Morning! Oh — you must be the new analyst. Brilliant, we've been expecting you. I'm Charlotte. Just so you know, Maya Chen has been in since before eight — first one through the door every single morning, honestly, without fail.": "/audio/receptionist_4b9ee40c.wav",
  "receptionist|Quick heads-up though — there's been a bit of a situation with the data pipeline overnight, and the client demo is in under an hour. It's a bit all-hands this morning, so Maya will bring you up to speed. You haven't missed anything critical. Yet.": "/audio/receptionist_075b29ae.wav",
  "receptionist|Head straight through the barrier on your left — analytics pod, first cluster of desks. Maya's the one who looks like she hasn't slept. Trust me, that does narrow it down to one person. Right — good luck. You are going to need it.": "/audio/receptionist_d918719a.wav",
  "maya|Oh thank god — you're actually here. I was starting to think I'd have to handle this alone.": "/audio/maya_66ff6eff.wav",
  "maya|The validation accuracy on the client demo model jumped from 82% to 94% overnight. A twelve-point leap. Oliver has already put that number on the sales deck.": "/audio/maya_fd83cda2.wav",
  "maya|I flagged it on Slack at seven this morning. Three hours ago. No response from anyone. The demo is in forty-five minutes.": "/audio/maya_99c97939.wav",
  "maya|I printed this validation report this morning. Read page two.": "/audio/maya_69513571.wav",
  "maya|See that? 1,460 rows flagged as potential duplicates. Out of 12,000 in the validation set. If those are real duplicates, they are inflating the score.": "/audio/maya_dbad12ab.wav",
