  "oliver|Talk to Priya in compliance first. Go through the right channel.": "/audio/oliver_b0edf659.wav",
  "oliver|Smart. Keep your head down on day one.": "/audio/oliver_ad326c2a.wav",
  "oliver|Still — talk to Priya before you leave the floor.": "/audio/oliver_b8905b98.wav",
  "priya|I have been waiting for someone to come to me. The question is whether you have anything actually useful.": "/audio/priya_7d81ca1e.wav",
  "priya|Do not give me emotions. Do not give me politics. Give me facts — structured, quantified, with named parties.": "/audio/priya_8820ad1f.wav",
  "priya|What changed, when did it change, who is aware of it, how material is the uncertainty, and what is the firm about to present to the client?": "/audio/priya_cf66069f.wav",
  "priya|And I need to know: has anyone in a senior position told you explicitly not to escalate this?": "/audio/priya_ce5aa765.wav",
  "priya|Because if they have, that is a separate compliance concern. Think carefully before you answer.": "/audio/priya_8f50ff53.wav",
  "priya|Good. I'm preparing a written memo now — it goes on record whether the demo proceeds or not.": "/audio/priya_cb9b128e.wav",
  "priya|Final call has to come from Amara Vale. Executive suite, north-east corner. Go now — twelve minutes.": "/audio/priya_57909920.wav",
